ygData.subject: Help needed from players of ALL servers!
ygData.msgSnippet: The Everquest SG player list hasnt been updated for months already, and with the release of Ruins of Kunark there has been an increase in the number of players
ygData.messageBody:
The Everquest SG player list hasnt been updated for months already, and
with the release of Ruins of Kunark there has been an increase in the
number of players in alot of servers, so I think its time for us to update
this list again. Please state your Chr's Nick(if U changed ur primary char
pls use that), race, class and Server you play in.Thx in Advance! This is
the list which I managed to dig out from my emails, so its quite old
already. Update it pls. There's alot of new SG players not in our eq
mailing list so pls update for them as well if U know their info. Thanks!
I've updated some of those in innoruuk server but I know there's alot more
if anyone has their info pls post.
